<xsl:if test="not(string($productId))"> <xsl:message terminate="yes"><xsl:value-of select="concat('Nebyl nalezen produkt dle EAN ', article_ean, ' v dokladu ', $userdocid, '. Ceník: ', AS:LookupValue('2fff47e8-a10d-4cbf-89dc-cf607ec7cc04', $priceListId))"/></xsl:message> </xsl:if>

SchemaItem.Name: Delivery_2_EDI
SchemaItem.M01:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?> <xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" version="1.0" xmlns:AS="http://schema.advantages.cz/AsapFunctions" xmlns:date="http://exslt.org/dates-and-times" exclude-result-prefixes="AS date">
<xsl:param name="senderEDI_ID"/> <xsl:param name="supplier_party_ean"/> <xsl:param name="supplier_business_name_1"/>
<xsl:key name="sscc" match="/ROOT/Delivery/DeliveryDetail/DeliveryDetailItem" use="concat(../@refDeliveryId, @SSCC)" /> <xsl:key name="product" match="/ROOT/Delivery/DeliveryDetail/DeliveryDetailItem" use="concat(../@refDeliveryId, @SSCC, ../@refProductId)" />
<xsl:template match="ROOT"> <biztalk_1> <xsl:apply-templates select="Delivery"/> </biztalk_1> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="Delivery"> <xsl:message><xsl:value-of select="AS:InitPosition(@Id, 0)"/></xsl:message>
<xsl:variable name="recipientEAN" select="AS:LookupValue('6310ab85-6fc1-4668-9fa1-60c61a7c695b', @refBusinessPartnerId)"/> <xsl:variable name="crossdockingAddressId" select="AS:LookupValue('d294eca8-1dc8-4ba9-959a-9450494e7897', 'BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannel_parBusinessPartnerId', @refBusinessPartnerId, 'BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannel_parBusinessPartnerCommunicationChannelTypeId', AS:GetConstant('BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannelType_EDI_AddressCrossdocking'))"/> <xsl:variable name="recipientAddressSet"> <xsl:choose> <xsl:when test="string($crossdockingAddressId)"> <AddressEAN> <xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('4651e5c5-f0a9-4faa-8adc-020f2f425afe', $crossdockingAddressId)"/> </AddressEAN> <AddressName> <xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('ec8cbc3a-73d7-461c-a54e-e55abad01d07', $crossdockingAddressId)"/> </AddressName> </xsl:when> <xsl:otherwise> <AddressEAN> <xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('4651e5c5-f0a9-4faa-8adc-020f2f425afe', @refBusinessPartnerCommunicationChannelId)"/> </AddressEAN> <AddressName> <xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('ec8cbc3a-73d7-461c-a54e-e55abad01d07', @refBusinessPartnerCommunicationChannelId)"/> </AddressName> </xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose> </xsl:variable>
<xsl:variable name="orderingAddressId" select="AS:LookupValue('d294eca8-1dc8-4ba9-959a-9450494e7897', 'BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannel_parBusinessPartnerId', @refBusinessPartnerId, 'BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannel_parBusinessPartnerCommunicationChannelTypeId', AS:GetConstant('BusinessPartnerCommunicationChannelType_AddressOrdering'))"/> <xsl:variable name="orderingEAN"> <xsl:if test="string($orderingAddressId)"> <xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('4651e5c5-f0a9-4faa-8adc-020f2f425afe', $orderingAddressId)"/> </xsl:if> </xsl:variable> <xsl:variable name="customerContractNumber" select="AS:LookupValue('3d975659-e236-4103-9473-b748c1e719b2', @refContractDocumentId)"/>
<header> <delivery> <message/> <to> <state> <ediid><xsl:value-of select="$recipientEAN"/></ediid> </state> </to> <from> <state> <ediid><xsl:value-of select="$senderEDI_ID"/></ediid> </state> </from> <interchange/> </delivery> <manifest> <document> <userdocid><xsl:value-of select="@ReferenceCode"/></userdocid> <name>xml_document</name> </document> </manifest> </header>
<body> <xml_document type_identifier="DESADV" version="1.2014"> <form_header> <userdocid><xsl:value-of select="@ReferenceCode"/></userdocid> <document_date><xsl:value-of select="substring-before(@DeliveryDate, 'T')"/></document_date> <date_of_delivery><xsl:value-of select="substring-before(@DeliveryDate, 'T')"/></date_of_delivery> <transport>Dodavatel</transport> <buyer_ean><xsl:value-of select="$recipientEAN"/></buyer_ean> <buyer_name><xsl:value-of select="@BusinessPartnerName"/></buyer_name> <delivery_place_ean><xsl:value-of select="AS:NodeSet($recipientAddressSet)/AddressEAN"/></delivery_place_ean> <delivery_place_name><xsl:value-of select="AS:NodeSet($recipientAddressSet)/AddressName"/></delivery_place_name> <supplier_ean><xsl:value-of select="$supplier_party_ean"/></supplier_ean> <supplier_name><xsl:value-of select="$supplier_business_name_1"/></supplier_name> <xsl:if test="string($orderingEAN)"> <orderedby_ean><xsl:value-of select="$orderingEAN"/></orderedby_ean> </xsl:if> </form_header>
<xsl:choose> <xsl:when test="@IsSSCCPrinted = 'true'"> <package_items> <xsl:apply-templates select="DeliveryDetail/DeliveryDetailItem[generate-id(.)=generate-id(key('sscc', concat(../@refDeliveryId, @SSCC))[1])]"> <xsl:with-param name="customerContractNumber" select="$customerContractNumber"/> </xsl:apply-templates> </package_items> </xsl:when> <xsl:otherwise> <line_items> <xsl:apply-templates select="DeliveryDetail"> <xsl:with-param name="customerContractNumber" select="$customerContractNumber"/> </xsl:apply-templates> </line_items> </xsl:otherwise> </xsl:choose> </xml_document> </body> <xsl:message><xsl:value-of select="AS:DestroyPosition(@Id)"/></xsl:message> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="DeliveryDetail"> <xsl:param name="customerContractNumber"/> <xsl:param name="quantity" select="@QuantityDelivered"/>
<item> <item_number><xsl:value-of select="AS:NextPosition(@refDeliveryId, 1)"/></item_number> <xsl:if test="string(@refProductId)"> <article_ean><xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('c637e15b-6d9c-48f0-b596-3c040816b265', @refProductId)"/></article_ean> <article_name><xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('2ca0c125-060d-4c64-9f25-80d5469fb093', @refProductId)"/></article_name> <article_number><xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('a3eabe74-2fca-4e98-9af0-3614a74f574d', @refProductId)"/></article_number> </xsl:if> <xsl:if test="string(@refContractDocumentBillingDetailId)"> <price><xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('32999db2-5af2-44c1-b40b-136a8902f14e', @refContractDocumentBillingDetailId)"/></price> <vat><xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('a3b7c6fe-f4cb-4b14-b980-a9ddc063b106', @refContractDocumentBillingDetailId)"/></vat> </xsl:if> <quantity><xsl:value-of select="$quantity"/></quantity> <xsl:if test="string(@refUomId)"> <unit><xsl:value-of select="AS:LookupValue('da134e3d-abd9-4d47-bfdf-0cf058699b1d', @refUomId)"/></unit> </xsl:if> <xsl:if test="string($customerContractNumber)"> <order_number><xsl:value-of select="$customerContractNumber"/></order_number> </xsl:if> </item> </xsl:template>
<xsl:template match="DeliveryDetailItem"> <xsl:param name="customerContractNumber"/>
<xsl:variable name="items" select="key('sscc', concat(../@refDeliveryId, @SSCC))"/> <package> <package_item_number><xsl:value-of select="position()"/></package_item_number> <package_type>200</package_type> <sscc_number><xsl:value-of select="@SSCC"/></sscc_number> <line_items> <xsl:message><xsl:value-of select="AS:Trace(concat(@SSCC, ': ', count($items)))"/></xsl:message> <xsl:for-each select="$items"> <xsl:sort select="../@refProductId"/> <xsl:variable name="deliveryId" select="../@refDeliveryId"/> <xsl:variable name="productId" select="../@refProductId"/> <xsl:variable name="sscc" select="@SSCC"/> <!--<xsl:message><xsl:value-of select="AS:Trace(concat(' ', $productId, ': ', count(preceding-sibling::*[../@refDeliveryId = $deliveryId and @SSCC = $sscc and ../@refProductId = $productId])))"/></xsl:message> --> <xsl:if test="count(preceding-sibling::*[../@refDeliveryId = $deliveryId and @SSCC = $sscc and ../@refProductId = $productId]) = 0"> <xsl:apply-templates select=".."> <xsl:with-param name="customerContractNumber" select="$customerContractNumber"/> <xsl:with-param name="quantity" select="@Quantity + AS:sum(following-sibling::*[../@refDeliveryId = $deliveryId and @SSCC = $sscc and ../@refProductId = $productId]/@Quantity)"/> </xsl:apply-templates> </xsl:if> </xsl:for-each> </line_items> </package> </xsl:template> </xsl:stylesheet>
